		{
			"name": "User Filtering Guide",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "📚 User Filtering Documentation",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/users/",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["users", ""]
						},
						"description": "📋 **USER FILTERING GUIDE**\n\n**Available Query Parameters:**\n\n1. **role_id** (integer): Filter by user role\n   - 1 = Enumerator (Data Collector)\n   - 2 = Checker (Data Reviewer)\n   - 3 = Admin (System Administrator)\n\n2. **status_id** (integer): Filter by user account status\n   - 1 = Active\n   - 2 = Inactive\n   - 3 = Suspended\n\n3. **email** (string): Partial email match (case-insensitive)\n   - Example: `?email=admin` finds users with 'admin' in email\n\n4. **jamatkhana_id** (string): Filter by assigned JamatKhana\n   - Returns users assigned to specific religious center\n\n5. **skip** (integer): Pagination offset (default: 0)\n   - Number of records to skip\n\n6. **limit** (integer): Maximum records to return (default: 10, max: 100)\n\n**Filter Combinations Examples:**\n\n- `?role_id=1&status_id=1` = Active Enumerators\n- `?email=john&limit=20` = Users with 'john' in email, max 20 results\n- `?jamatkhana_id=JK001&role_id=1` = Enumerators assigned to JK001\n- `?skip=20&limit=10` = Page 3 (records 21-30)\n\n**Response Format:**\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"Id\": \"USER_12345678\",\n    \"Email\": \"user@example.com\",\n    \"FullName\": \"User Name\",\n    \"PhoneNumber\": \"+1234567890\",\n    \"RoleId\": 1,\n    \"StatusId\": 1,\n    \"JamatKhanaIds\": [\"JK001\"],\n    \"IsActive\": true,\n    \"CreatedAt\": \"2024-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\n    \"UpdatedAt\": \"2024-01-01T00:00:00Z\"\n  }\n]\n```"
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "🔍 Advanced User Search Examples",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/users/",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["users", ""]
						},
						"description": "🔍 **ADVANCED SEARCH EXAMPLES**\n\n**1. Find All Active Enumerators:**\n`GET /users/?role_id=1&status_id=1`\n\n**2. Find Users by Email Pattern:**\n`GET /users/?email=@gmail.com`\n\n**3. Find Users in Specific JamatKhana with Pagination:**\n`GET /users/?jamatkhana_id=JK001&skip=0&limit=50`\n\n**4. Find Inactive Admins:**\n`GET /users/?role_id=3&status_id=2`\n\n**5. Find Users by Name Pattern (via Email):**\n`GET /users/?email=john.doe`\n\n**6. Get First 100 Users:**\n`GET /users/?limit=100`\n\n**7. Get Users from Page 5 (50 per page):**\n`GET /users/?skip=200&limit=50`\n\n**8. Find Checkers in Multiple JamatKhanas:**\n`GET /users/?role_id=2&jamatkhana_id=JK001`\n\n**Performance Tips:**\n- Use specific filters to reduce result set\n- Combine filters for precise searches\n- Use pagination for large datasets\n- Avoid very broad searches without limits"
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		},
